1398, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But can anyone pull off the sporting hero staple?\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting hero staple\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Abroad, colourful-mirror wrap-around shades come two-a-penny on beaches, as salesmen walk about flogging them at \\u20ac10 a pop.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"colourful-mirror wrap-around shades\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"beaches\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"salesmen\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Brits might have remained reserved in their choices (you would sooner see a family kitted out in theirRay Bans Wayfarers, than anything more abrupt), our European counterparts needed no persuasion to lean in.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brits\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"their choices\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"theirRay Bans Wayfarers\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"our European counterparts\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"no persuasion\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, they might have been keeping a closer eye on the Spring Summer 2024 fashion month circuit, where a handful of labels put money on the style winning this year's race.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a closer eye\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the Spring Summer 2024 fashion month circuit\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"labels\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \